{"type": "article", "id": 24365, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-24T07:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 16018, "name": "hem"}, {"id": 25315, "name": "D-NAMIC"}, {"id": 25316, "name": "Esrawe"}, {"id": 25317, "name": "Studio Make Sense"}, {"id": 24381, "name": "Stitch Design Co."}, {"id": 16668, "name": "Max Lamb"}, {"id": 25318, "name": "Marek Krupa"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104134HurjCJs80Rw2zFM6.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Stool Splatter seats by Max Lamb &amp; Hem</h2>\n<p>这是一把由金属制作的凳子，它的造型非常简单，有点像倒扣起来的桶，似乎可以感受到凳子旋转起来的轻盈。在凳子的最上面有一圈凹进去的纹路，突出了座位的特征。整体喷上了细密的圆点，有黑与白、绿与粉这类反差较大的对比，色彩跳跃而有活力，也有蓝和白、粉和白这样较清新的搭配，都很有个性，是英国设计师为家具品牌 Hem 设计，目前还没有上市。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160114shIMu4OAnJGwozRg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160114TpBknsKYwAoSWN5Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09508547\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061601150G7ELeHnxU53i9JS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99893162\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160116M7pOUewtxT0G5RuA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.14529915\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160116Ws9kJMNzRy0p4nj8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Pet On Wheels by D-NAMIC</h2>\n<p>意大利工作室 D-NAMIC 为宠物狗设计了一个可固定于自行车或摩托车车后的小窝，主体是用塑料做的，里面带有靠背和软垫。特别在于它有一个圆形的孔，可以将头伸出来，当你觉得无暇顾及它的安全时也可以手提着小窝。它有 11 种颜色可选，目前已完成众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/d-namic/pow-pet-on-wheels/description\">这里是众筹链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160117qyInJxl3EudSW7Ab.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160117Gid2L8JBXsIkuPyw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160118GK6oUjsDOiurJCW5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160118jp2KVsMdkylL3bmJ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73529412\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061601196lEe4rWOyXCZTaM9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>brass and wood lights by Esrawe</h2>\n<p>这组灯是用木头和黄铜做的，它们都通过滑动来控制开关。落地灯以圆形金属片和两个小圆柱为支点，从其中一个支点换到另一个支点时就完成了开关。其余三盏桌灯与此同理，可以滑动圆形金属或者木头本身，增加了人与灯的互动和联系，也让最日常的东西多了一份趣味。设计者来自墨西哥，<a href=\"http://www.esrawe.com/product/prima-materia/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160119bwh7FOrPQiHxsIYk.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.13034188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160120VwAPdOsU71h4aBQf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160120b825sSie4H3CZTkt.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061601215HGzJ6NPO2QVvWo8.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160122KeL7QAj14vxYyhIr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65064103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160122qISWwFDr6JVe3Cgn.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>SORTSAGE by Studio Make Sense</h2>\n<p>存钱罐似乎很少使用，但放零碎硬币的盒子倒是很常见。泰国设计工作室 Studio Make Sense 发明了一个可以将硬币按大小分类的木盒子，投放硬币的孔后面是一个斜坡滑梯，按照银币的大小做了漏孔，对应了四个筒，这样不同的硬币就能集中掉进自己的筒里了。如果需要取出硬币，就把盒子打开。对于硬币种类更丰富的地方来说很实用。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160123oAbGMQwUcSfYdWkt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160124ME5RqvhglyWi1eNs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160124vX2giI8MVDKm5AdS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060616012530jsu1AXWvibJLxg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061601253ZplN6GcDJwKsW8M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.85452323\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061601257FfEsuaWXdI5NZ3L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.855\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"></div>\n<h2>Ration by Marek Krupa</h2>\n<p>这是一个咖啡过滤器，它一共有三层，每一层盒子都是一道过滤网，你需要将磨碎后咖啡豆倒入最上面一层盒子里，然后摇动整个盒子使碎末分层，就可以筛选出细末状的和石头块（boulders）的，其中细末状是口感最好的，而那些像石头块一样凝固的只能增加苦味。过滤器的过滤层是可替换的，产品目前在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/rafino/the-rafino-coffee-grind-refining-system?token=070c7081\">这里是众筹链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160126c5x1tgyvnYz8MCPH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160126nPLG9aVcMOb4izuS.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160128CRUPLZnTpdl9Hocy.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160129LqUbHvE0MRFrsaDk.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160131BKIQ5VugdJ4N6nqc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<h2>REWIND SOAP by Stitch Design Co.</h2>\n<p>这个香皂包装最明显的特征是上面的蜡印，常用于信封封口而像一个小的浮雕，立刻让包装拥有古典的优雅。蜡印盖在纸壳和一层很薄的木料之间，木料上用印刷体居中写下了相应的文字，给人一种阅读的感觉，也体现出这款香皂的精致和贵重。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061601328RSs9NnB2JXHiL0U.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160132zAUKeCVtIc49NYZs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160133rVpAKlUjZMR2iuoQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160134lKWAjVtPh1g6UMLm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160134KJ5YSRFuGpZ1aB9h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.51092896\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}